{"page_id": 20133, "slug": "Evangelion_Anima_2010_06", "title": "Evangelion Anima 2010 06", "display_title": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Evangelion Anima 2010 06</span>", "namespace": 0, "content_model": "wikitext", "language": null, "wikitext": "{{Template:Expand}}\n{{Template: Translation}}\n\nThis is the ninth chapter of the second part of [[Evangelion Anima]] published in the June 2010 issue of Dengeki Hobby Magazine. \n\n==Original Japanese Text==\n\n[[Image:Anima_2010_06_S2_Chapter09_193.jpg|thumb|right|150px|\"Page 193 illustration by Hiroyuki Utatane\"]]\n\n[[Category:Anima]]\n[[Category:Translations]]\n[[Category:Publications]]", "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table align=\"center\" style=\"border:2px solid lightseagreen; width:85%; background:honeydew;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/180px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"101\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/270px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/360px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 2x\" /></a></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<p><big><b>\"<i>Making something... Nurturing something is really great. You can see and learn so many things from the process.</i>\"</b></big><br />\nPlease help improve this article or section by <b>expanding it.</b><br />\n<small>If you have questions on what to improve/expand, please discuss on the talk page.</small>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border:2px solid orangered; width:85%; background:oldlace;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:01_C156_big.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/9/92/01_C156_big.jpg/135px-01_C156_big.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"135\" height=\"101\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/92/01_C156_big.jpg/203px-01_C156_big.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/92/01_C156_big.jpg/270px-01_C156_big.jpg 2x\" /></a></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<p><big><b>\"<i>You mean you couldn't read the questions in Japanese?</i>\" \"<i>Right, I haven't learned all the Chinese characters yet. We didn't study it in college over there.</i>\"</b><br /></big>\nThis page or section is in need of an <b>accurate translation</b>. Please help out if you know Japanese! (This is meant to be informative since chances of an official translation are slim.)<br />\n<small>Please edit this article or discuss this issue on the talk page.</small><br />\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>This is the ninth chapter of the second part of <a href=\"/Evangelion_Anima\" title=\"Evangelion Anima\">Evangelion Anima</a> published in the June 2010 issue of Dengeki Hobby Magazine. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Original_Japanese_Text\">Original Japanese Text</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Evangelion_Anima_2010_06&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Original Japanese Text\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Anima_2010_06_S2_Chapter09_193.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/Anima_2010_06_S2_Chapter09_193.jpg/150px-Anima_2010_06_S2_Chapter09_193.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"206\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/Anima_2010_06_S2_Chapter09_193.jpg/225px-Anima_2010_06_S2_Chapter09_193.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e6/Anima_2010_06_S2_Chapter09_193.jpg/300px-Anima_2010_06_S2_Chapter09_193.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>\"Page 193 illustration by Hiroyuki Utatane\"</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260416205157\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.010 se